WEBVTT

00:01.359 --> 00:03.480
Harriet Lennox,
I want you gone!

00:03.560 --> 00:04.840
If you doubt
your man's affections,

00:04.960 --> 00:05.840
it's not because of me.

00:05.960 --> 00:07.400
‐You've gone your own way,

00:07.480 --> 00:08.800
Margaret, always.

00:08.880 --> 00:10.080
Now I'll go mine.

00:10.160 --> 00:12.160
Lydia Quigley, this is
a warrant for your arrest.

00:14.080 --> 00:17.840
‐Pursue Mrs. Quigley
at your peril.

00:17.960 --> 00:19.760
‐You must have
benefactors somewhere.

00:19.800 --> 00:21.160
‐Lady Fitz.

00:21.200 --> 00:23.920
<i>Isabella Fitzwilliam,</i>
<i>heiress of Blayne.</i>

00:24.000 --> 00:25.640
<i>The finest jewel of all.</i>

00:25.760 --> 00:27.480
‐You're speaking
against Mrs. Quigley?

00:27.520 --> 00:28.480
I can help you.

00:28.600 --> 00:30.160
<i>‐One day she'll let down</i>
<i>her guard.</i>

00:30.200 --> 00:32.560
When I'm done, Mrs. Quigley
will be dust and ash.

00:32.640 --> 00:35.640
I'll speak but no one
can know it came from me.

00:35.680 --> 00:37.320
‐We've got her.
‐Fuck me.

00:39.000 --> 00:45.074
